values:
14th november is my mother's birthday...
i wanna celebrate her birthday with her...
but it's wednesday so i need to go back to my campus - bird cage...
it was really a boring place...
oh my god...
i hate that place...
arghhhhhhhhhhhh...

17th december is my final term exam...
oh my god...
i really can't finish my syllabus...
it's a lot and i am gonna be crazy...
lolx...
anyway, i must work harder...
my 1st term and 2nd term result sucks...
so i need to work very very very very very extremely hard...

it was a deepavali holiday...
1 week only...
it really pass so fast...
the whole week have been studying but really cannot finish...
haiz...
wat to do, still need to study right...
feel so lazy...
and it was really a terrible holiday for me...
on deepavali, when i was sleeping at night...
the fireworks really make me can't sleep at all...
and i am gonna be a big panda...
my grandmother was really sick...
she vomit blood and d stupid dr say is just a small case...
how could it be if someone vomit blood??
anyway, my grandma is better now...
thank god...
another thing is my aunt's father passed away in an accident...
he was already 87 years old...
it was 6am and he is walking alone to the market...
so pity...
AND...
my mother say that my hair was soooooooooo messy and want me to cut it...
so i went, the hairdresser change a new hairstyle for me...
he says that it was nice but it really look like a mushroom...
oh my god..
is tat terrible enough...

Today, I am back at home...
Hooray...
I am so happy to be at home...
I miss my home although I come back every week...
Before I reach home, I went to Pacific to TC Tan...
My spectacles are calar again...
I change my frame also...
It is a combination of dark green, yellow and orange...
It looks cool...
Hihi...
People will think I am crazy enough...
Haha...
